---
import RegisterButton from './RegisterButton.astro';
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div>
      <span class="hero-chip">A 501(c)(3) nonprofit</span>
      <h1>Speedskating<br>is for <em>everyone</em><br>in our community</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Let's Skate Foundation is dedicated to promoting speedskating and making
        the sport accessible across the United States. It partners with local
        school districts to bring speedskating to all community youth aged 4–18.
        Collaborating with local US Speedskating clubs, the foundation hosts
        interscholastic competitions to reintroduce speedskating into school
        communities, while offering comprehensive programs and resources to
        support the multi-dimensional growth of the sport.
      </p>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        First launched in 2021 within the Elmbrook School District as the
        nation's current only school-district-based speedskating club, the model
        achieved remarkable success and officially evolved into the
        Let's Skate Foundation in 2024.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-btns">
        <RegisterButton variant="primary" label="Register for 2026 Let's Skate Summer Camp" href="https://www.speedskatingevents.org/2026letsskate"/>
        <a href="/about" class="btn-outline">Learn our story</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-photos" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="hero-photo-card hero-photo-card--top">
        <img src="/skate-photo-1.jpeg" alt="Skaters at Elmbrook Speedskating" />
      </div>
      <div class="hero-photo-card hero-photo-card--bottom">
        <img src="/skate-photo-2.jpeg" alt="Skaters at Elmbrook Speedskating" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  :global(.hero h1) {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
  }
  :global(.hero-sub) {
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  :global(.hero-sub:last-of-type) {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .hero-photos {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .hero-photo-card {
    border-radius: 18px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.14);
    width: 100%;
    height: 290px;
  }
  .hero-photo-card img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .hero-photos {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
